《'''巴伦周刊'''》（{{lang-en|''Barron's''}}）<ref name="蒙克2005">{{cite book|author=蒙克|title=抢滩传媒的傻子们|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0k8uOJh3wDYC&pg=PA119|year=2005|publisher=中信出版社|isbn=978-7-5086-0437-4|pages=119–|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922070212/https://books.google.com/books?id=0k8uOJh3wDYC&pg=PA119|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一份由[[新闻集团|新闻集团]]旗下的[[道琼斯公司|道琼斯公司]]出版的[[美国国旗|美国]][[周刊|周刊]]与[[报纸|报纸]]，由[[克拉伦斯·巴伦|克拉伦斯·巴伦]]（Clarence Barron，1855-1928<ref name=Clarence.NYT>{{cite newspaper|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1928/10/03/archives/clarence-w-barron-publisher-is-dead-head-of-the-wall-st-journal-a.html|title=CLARENCE W. BARRON, PUBLISHER, IS DEAD; Head of The Wall St. Journal a Victim of Catarrhal Jaundice at 73 in Battle Creek. NOTED FINANCIAL FIGURE A Writer on World Fiscal Topics --Body Will Be Taken to His Old Home in Boston.|date=1928-10-03|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818123342/https://www.nytimes.com/1928/10/03/archives/clarence-w-barron-publisher-is-dead-head-of-the-wall-st-journal-a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>）于1921年创办，时名《[[巴伦氏全国商业与金融周报|巴伦氏全国商业与金融周报]]》（Barron's National Business and Financial Weekly）<ref>{{cite book|title=新闻学|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-KErAAAAMAAJ|year=1985|publisher=中国人民大学书报资料社|pages=89-|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922035232/https://books.google.com/books?id=-KErAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》的[[姊妹|姊妹]][[刊物|刊物]]<ref name="Tuccille2003">{{cite book|author=Jerome Tuccille|title=How to Profit from the Wall Street Mergers: Riding the Takeover Wave|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CBIb19aZ91AC&pg=PA15|year=2003|publisher=Beard Books|isbn=978-1-58798-220-0|pages=15–|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712023035/https://books.google.com/books?id=CBIb19aZ91AC&pg=PA15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

